The paper deals with image recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The proposed model is a deep learning model that involves training on both labeled and unlabeled data, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The paper also discusses the use of label embeddings, which is a technique commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
